definitions.definition: Any of several species of fish in Salmonidae, closely related to salmon, and distinguished by spawning more than once.
definitions.example: Many anglers consider trout to be the archetypical quarry.
Look, you silly old trout, you can't keep bringing home cats! You can't afford the ones you have!

definitions.definition: To (figuratively) slap someone with a slimy, stinky, wet trout; to admonish jocularly.
